Target Image Analysis:
- Structure: Two orange cylindrical blocks supporting a green rectangular block
- Layers: 2 layers (cylinders at bottom, rectangular block on top)
- Spatial Arrangement: Two cylinders positioned parallel to each other, with a green block spanning across their top

Block Selection:
- Green rectangular block (appears to be from index 2)
- Two orange cylindrical blocks (from indices 8 and 9)

Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 8 (orange cylinder)
    Step2: Move block with index 9 (orange cylinder)
    Step3: Move block with index 2 (green rectangular block)
}

The assembly follows the structure shown in the main target image, with the two orange cylindrical blocks placed parallel to each other and the green rectangular block positioned across their top surfaces.
